{"tid":1308122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杯葛 合興集團旗下所有牌子：吉野家、駱駝嘜、超羣","createTime":"2019-07-11T21:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T07:51:52.000Z","uid":50275,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"45edb282c5fef7e8ac349729878707658c608e86","tid":1308122,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eadetq5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feadetq5.jpg&h=51259427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港合興集團有限公司總裁洪明基昨日知悉事件後表示極為憤怒，已和涉事的外判廣告公司解約，並解僱負責廣告事務的公司員工。 <br />\n<br />\n對旗下企業吉野家發佈疑似「辱警」廣告，洪明基昨日表示事先並不知情，對此極為憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，自己近期剛剛參加了撐警大會，全力支持特區政府依法施政，就發生此事非常痛心。目前該廣告已經刪除，涉事的外判廣告公司已經解約，負責廣告事務的公司員工已被解聘。<br />\n_____________________________________________<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全国政协委员</span>、香港洪氏集团副董事长、合兴集团控股有限公司行政总裁洪明基<br />\n全国政协委员<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eDTVcye.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeDTVcye.png&h=0cc4b489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n_____________________________________________"},{"pid":"248c520b72cf95061066ebd0b1c49e00c61144c3","tid":1308122,"uid":50275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:10:29.000Z","msg":"合興集團<br />\n<br />\n非執行董事包括：黃宜弘、石禮謙等。主要產品有花生油、粟米油、芥花籽油、橄欖油等，同時經營快餐、西餅等業務。<br />\n<br />\n在2011年12月1日，合興集團以34.75億港元，收購洪氏家族 Summerfield Profits Limited 股權，資產包括在中國東北及華北地區（包括北京、天津）兩家快餐連鎖店吉野家及Dairy Queen的特許經營權[1]。<br />\n<br />\n主要品牌<br />\n食用油：<br />\n<br />\n獅球嘜<br />\n駱駝嘜<br />\n麒麟<br />\n紅桃<br />\n喜鵲<br />\n盈樂<br />\n金鹿<br />\nSS上等食油<br />\n青島雙鴿<br />\n<br />\n西餅店：<br />\n超羣<br />\n<br />\n中國東北及華北地區連鎖店特許經營權：<br />\n<br />\n-吉野家（北京市、天津市、河北省、遼寧省、黑龍江省，吉林省，內蒙古自治區、河南、山西及陝西）<br />\n-Dairy Queen"},{"pid":"74e5689d05bcd5e384c5eabe93f940e649970dd1","tid":1308122,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f15f14bf0b8ecd0e4eea9fc6377c8fbf0af4276","tid":1308122,"uid":62270,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:19:07.000Z","msg":"88,吉野家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366f59cc729af1d3ac85d10131fa6d954e8fa762","tid":1308122,"uid":52366,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:26:22.000Z","msg":"罷食係唔夠架！！！ 要諗吓點樣制裁佢哋！<br />\n例如轟炸Facebook？ 寫信投訴？ <br />\n<br />\n有冇公司可以請咗吉野家小編<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e072010fcb1e6ad26b664dd7c7ddbb2dbcd3f3b","tid":1308122,"uid":199957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:32:52.000Z","msg":"大家幫手check下佢有冇屋企人係外國人拎外國護照啦<br />\n出席咗撐警集會仲唔快啲舉報"},{"pid":"f5958d2399d7a3fbf3aefb8142b7c43dffa022d1","tid":1308122,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:56:00.000Z","msg":"吉野家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2481c73276ce7307f80a395f6dff234a2c03a298","tid":1308122,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822db9fd3845561b7374dd50f26aea2ae4feb10e","tid":1308122,"uid":48020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:17:24.000Z","msg":"Send email 去日本總公司投訴有冇用？"},{"pid":"95e8d56294abe2c79a7430a1c4cf24df83bc1fb3","tid":1308122,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:35:50.000Z","msg":"吉野家上咗神台一日都冇就要落返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.g